lua 面向对象

冒号在面向对象中的含义：
	
通过两个例子来说明
(1) Accout = {balance = 0}
	function Accout.withDraw(self, v)
		self.balance = self.balance - v
	end
	a = Accout
	Accout = nil
	a.withDraw(a, 100)
	print(a.balance)

(2) Accout = {balance = 0}
	function Accout:withDraw(v)
		self.balance = self.balance - v
	end
	a = Accout
	Accout = nil
	a:withDraw(100)
	print(a.balance)

冒号的作用很简单，就是需要在定义方法时候加一个额外的隐藏参数